description:
*Is Disney Safe For Christians?* | Disney is a mastermind when it comes to creating seemingly family-friendly products. Whether it’s a film or a cartoon or an amusement park, Disney has convinced the masses that it’s simply good clean fun. But, at a closer examination, something more sinister is underneath that innocent persona… @disneychannel @DisneyMovieTrailers @disneyanimation
